overview.heading: Frisco Virtual Office
overview.body: Looking to give your startup or existing business a Frisco address but worried about the price tag of a full-fledged office? Opus VO has you covered. You can use one of our premium Frisco locations as your official business address without straining your budget. Plus, when you need a professional setting for meetings with clients or team discussions, our well-equipped conference rooms are at your service.  But that’s not all. When you opt for a virtual office with Opus VO in Frisco, you also get the support of a live receptionist. Our attentive team ensures that your clients always have a positive experience when they contact your business. We also manage daily office tasks like sorting your mail and directing your calls, so you can focus on growing your business.

faqs.question: Can I receive mail under my company name and personal name?
faqs.answer: Yes, you can receive mail under both once your account has been activated.

faqs.question: Do you use an automated phone service or a receptionist to answer?
faqs.answer: We offer a live, personalized receptionist to transfer your calls during business hours Monday to Friday. Calls made after hours will be met with a professional voicemail.

faqs.question: Can I have a virtual office in Frisco, Texas even if I don’t reside there?
faqs.answer: Yes, and it is a fantastic way to expand your presence to new clients. It will build trust with residents by having your business in the heart of Frisco. You can also adapt to better meet your clients’ unique needs within Texas.

faqs.question: What do you mean by “all-inclusive services”?
faqs.answer: Our Frisco virtual office offerings include all features listed at the same monthly cost, regardless of the location you choose. Please note that mail centers and some premium locations may not include all options. If you would like additional information, you can compare Opus to our competitors or contact us.

sections.title: Why Frisco? Why Opus VO?
sections.body: Why Frisco? Why Opus VO?  Frisco isn’t just a vibrant community to live in; it’s a bustling hub for business as well. It’s a smart choice for your business’s future growth.  Don’t hesitate; your next big business milestone could be just a phone call or a click away.  Opus VO, Frisco @ 6160 Warren Parkway, Frisco, TX 75034
